window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Ye screw with this lass, ye get put on yer ass.</p> <p>When Maxwell sends Team Trouble to investigate a series of unfortunate events, we discover that everything in Texas is bigger-including the mayhem.</p> <p>Between hexed hijinks, rodeo riots, and line-dancing drama, my team has its hands full . . .</p> <p>And that's before things really go to hell.</p> <p>When the baggage of disgruntled exes and slighted gods and goddesses get thrown into the mix, the violence of the empowered world hits way too close to home.</p> <p>But through it all, we find strength in the same place as always . . . in the love of family and friends.</p>"; 
